{
  "page": "A Consideration of History",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>A Consideration of History</b></i> is a history written by Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Perestan\" title=\"Perestan\">Perestan</a>. It includes the <a href=\"/index.php/War_Across_the_Water\" title=\"War Across the Water\">War Across the Water</a>, in which the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a> fought over the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The text also suggests \"<a href=\"/index.php/Erreg\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Erreg\">Erreg</a>\" was the corrupted title of an Andal chieftain who cut down <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwoods</a> on behalf of a <a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">river king</a>'s rival.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Consideration_of_History&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>For <a href=\"/index.php/War_Across_the_Water\" title=\"War Across the Water\">ten long centuries</a> <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">the direwolf</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"King of Mountain and Vale\">the falcon</a> had fought and bled over <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">three rocks</a>, until one day the wolf awoke as from a dream and realized it was only stone between his teeth, whence he spat it out and walked away.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Consideration_of_History&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403171041\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.024 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.052 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 268/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8697/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1207/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 567/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1353/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   45.700      1 -total\n 77.91%   35.606      1 Template:Italic_title\n 15.81%    7.225      3 Template:Ref\n  9.19%    4.201      3 Template:Ref/core\n  4.21%    1.925      1 Template:Quote\n  4.09%    1.871      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19899-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403171041 and revision id 239295\n -->\n",
